PrecisAmendment to the HIV - INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSISTANCE ORDER, enacted by Order in Council P.C. 1990-4/872 of May 10, 1990, which will extend the period during which applications for assistance will be accepted from January 1, 1991 to April 1, 1991.
